dc_title_s: The Balkans 1:250,000. Sremska Mitrovica, sheet Y-16. A.M.S. M506 (G.S.G.S. 4413)
dc_description_s: Great Britain. War Office. General Staff. Geographical Section. G.S.G.S. 4413. Bosnia and Herzegovina--Sremska Mitrovica Sheet. Alternate title: Sremska Mitrovica. Lambert conical orthomorphic projection. Danube zone grid. Relief shown by 50 and 100 meter contour intervals and and spot elevations. With a Serb and Croat glossary. Corrected from Intelligence reports up to March, 1944. Compiled and drawn by War Office, 1944. See index. Library holdings for this set are incomplete. Geographic designation is given as Yugoslavia it is Bosnia and Herzegovina, and Serbia and Montenegro.
dc_publisher_s: Washington, D.C. : Army Map Service, U.S. Army, 1949.
